# Algorithmic Eyewear by Jay Rosen Design

Welcome to the Algorithmic Eyewear repository. This project showcases a unique collection of eyewear designs, existing at the intersection of art, AI, and blockchain technology, by Jay Rosen Design.

## About the Project

**Algorithmic Eyewear** is a collection of 100 unique AI artworks, conceived and generated by Jay Rosen Design in March 2023. These pieces were created using **Midjourney 4**, with the AI model trained on Jay Rosen Design's innovative **Mirror Visionwear**.

The primary impetus for this collection was its development for the **UF Blockchain Lab NFT Contest**, where it proudly secured the **1st place award**.

These explorations delve into:
* **AI-Generated Art:** Leveraging cutting-edge text-to-image AI to produce novel visual concepts.
* **Conceptual Eyewear:** Pushing the boundaries of traditional eyewear design into the realm of digital art and futuristic aesthetics.
* **NFTs (Non-Fungible Tokens):** Representing each unique artwork as a verifiable digital asset on the blockchain.

## Achievements and Exhibitions

The Algorithmic Eyewear collection has been recognized and showcased in several prominent digital and physical art spaces:

* **Metaverse Fashion Week:** Displayed in Decentraland (70, 29) at the Mirror Vision Gallery.
    ![Mirror Vision Gallery at Metaverse Fashion Week](https://github.com/jayrosen-design/Algorithmic-Eyewear/blob/main/mirror-vision-gallery-banner-copy-1024x576.png?raw=true)

* **1st Place Winner:** UF Blockchain Lab NFT Contest (2023).
    ![UF Blockchain Lab NFT Contest Winners](https://github.com/jayrosen-design/Algorithmic-Eyewear/blob/main/nft-contest-2023.jpg?raw=true)

* **Wynwood Miami NFT Art Show:** Exhibited at HODLER Gallery.
  ![Wynwood Miami NFT Art Show](https://github.com/jayrosen-design/Algorithmic-Eyewear/blob/main/nft-miami-2023.jpg?raw=true)



## NFT Collection

The Algorithmic Eyewear collection consists of 100 unique NFTs. These are available for minting on the Ethereum blockchain.

* **Platform:** OpenSea
* **Price:** 0.10 ETH
* **Link:** [Algorithmic Eyewear on OpenSea](https://opensea.io/collection/algorithmic-eyewear)
